snippet.title: Monty Python's Flying Circus gameplay (PC Game, 1990)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Monty Python's Flying Circus, Dos PC game produced by Core Design in 1990 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/monty-python-s-flying-circus/4944/
Playing through this surreal platformer based on the classic TV series.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
